cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentence representation learning. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves training neural networks and learning representations. Additionally, it could be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of recurrent neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it deals with multi-view learning, which is a common technique in computer vision.
